description:
Welcome to Holiday Inn Tabuk!
Friendly service and warm welcome are our everyday policy to our guests. Our guest service associates will ensure that your visit is a very pleasant and memorable one.
&nbsp;
The hotel is only 3km from Tabuk Regional Airport. Stay your way with the modern amenities you expect and the style you want. Holiday Inn Tabuk offers dining experiences that are delightful and delicious. We offer elegant services via Al Walima Restaurant which offers wide range of oriental and western food in a nice atmosphere.
&nbsp;
Whatever your needs are, we can accommodate. With all of our exclusive offers, we'll inspire everything from successful business travels to memorable holiday vacations. 
&nbsp;
We thank you for choosing Holiday Inn Tabuk. Wish you a pleasant staying with us.
